		<p><p>Yves Roubaud, a native of Martigues, France, trained at the Culinary Institute of Provence as well as several French restaurants in the Mediterranean port city of Marseilles and in Cannes. He joined Lettuce Entertain You Enterprises (LEYE) in 1980, when he first served as sous chef at Ambria and manager of Un Grand CafÃ©.</p>

